search_results.title: Hathor - Explore Deities of Ancient Egypt
search_results.snippet: Hathor was one of the forty-two state gods and goddesses of Egypt, and one of the most popular and powerful. She was goddess of many things.

search_results.title: Hathor Rising: The Power of the Goddess in Ancient Egypt
search_results.snippet: The first book to seriously examine the feminine aspect of Egyptian religion sheds new light on the important role of the goddess Hathor-Sekhmet.
